      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6696735/" class="title-link">我读到的最好的译本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6696735"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/60889088/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u60889088-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/60889088/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">石客</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-06-09"
      class="main-meta">2014-06-09 15:42:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6696735_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是我读到的最好的译本，译者已经走进作者的文字里去，其前言，在形式和内容上都有些基尔克果“附身”的感觉。而且这本《恐惧与战栗》属于“经典与解释”丛书，文本与解读并重，不仅有原作译本，还有“附录”部分的解读可参考。非常精彩！ 

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            华夏出版社2013版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
