  <div class="indent">
    <ul>
        <li class="mb8 pl">
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1007655/">贵州人民出版社版</a>
          1994-04 / 297人读过 / 有售
        </li>
        <li class="mb8 pl">
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1757676/">Penguin Classics版</a>
          1986-1-7 / 43人读过
